OOC: This is the only thing I learned at the Boston science museum.

::Firaxis::
       He curled up in a ball and allowed the electricity to flow over his 
casing without damaging his internal circuitry.  "Can you give me one good 
reason I should help you?"  He grimaces as scorch marks appear on his armor.
